{"tid":2418501,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IZ*ONE粉絲聯合發表延長支持聲明書","createTime":"2021-02-22T16:02:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T10:18:02.000Z","uid":1086,"like":9,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7b9f0c89652f6c5a50a2dc277c71da03e6822069","tid":2418501,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T16:02:22.000Z","msg":"在CJ ENM方面通過輿論公開了關於IZ*ONE簽約延長的事項所屬社和成員們正在商議中的主張之後，時間已經流逝了一個月，不知不覺已到了IZ*ONE離活動結束只剩兩個月的時間點了。<br />\nIZ*ONE粉絲聯合一直在等待著CJ ENM發表IZ*ONE將繼續活動的決定。並且IZ*ONE粉絲聯合已準備好積極支持活動延長的發表，正等待著肯定性的消息。<br />\n對此，IZ*ONE粉絲聯合請求下列事項：<br />\n<br />\n1. IZ*ONE粉絲聯合請求CJ ENM及所屬社方面推動IZ*ONE進行持續且不變的12人團體活動。<br />\n2. 請求CJ ENM及所屬社在之後IZ*ONE的組合活動中也給予全力支持。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>最後，除了本聲明書之外的所有聲明書都不是IZ*ONE粉絲聯合的立場，IZ*ONE粉絲聯合始終不變地為IZ*ONE應援且支持。</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/otncDgO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FotncDgO.jpg&h=a2014dcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n堂堂正正IZ*ONE,對得起人 對得住神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1ee438f84567dff06491c4c49d30e9ba39773ee","tid":2418501,"uid":34489,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T16:04:05.000Z","msg":"永續izone..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e564963653ff178dc0fb8a062933566c2669dd4e","tid":2418501,"uid":1086,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T16:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2enoKXN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2enoKXN.jpg&h=9d524f82&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa90ba77f5c96a3c9348dc8c97ced05054648002","tid":2418501,"uid":1086,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T16:26:48.000Z","msg":"我問一句<br />\n冇左IZ*ONE,唔通你地要睇住BLACKPINK獨大咩,<br />\n明明大家都唔鍾意BLACKPINK,點解唔聯合力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" 